                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <locus target="#1v"/>
                     <title type="complete">Prayer against black Bāryā, evil demons, and all impure spirits for 
                        <ref type="pers" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS14672GabraKrestos">Gabra Krəstos</ref>.</title>
                     <note cert="high">The <foreign xml:lang="de">Vorlage</foreign> of this text is 
                        <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/UppEt1#a6">No item: UppEt1, could not check for a6</ref>.</note>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                        በስመ፡ አብ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis"/> ኀለሹን፡ ሸኀለሹን፡ 
                        ለሹን፡ ወበረሹን፡ ወለጬራሼን፡ በዝ፡ አስማቲከ፡ እስሮሙ፡ 
                        ለባርያ፡ ጸሊማን፡ ወለአጋንንት፡ ፀዋጋን፡ ወለኵሎሙ፡ መናፍስት፡ ርኩሣን፡
                        ሸሐሔ፡ እስራ፡ ፻፡ ፻፡ ርእስ፡ መጽሔት፡ በእኖን፡ በስመ፡ እኁን፡ በእግዚአብሔር፡ 
                        ንጉሥ፡ በሐዴን፡ በበንዴን፡ ክርስቶስ፡ ንጉሥ፡ በጨሽ፡ ቤጫዋሼ፡ በጫዋዩነ፡ 
                        ጨሺ፡ ዶዘርዘራ፡ ፀርየ፡ ወፀላእትየ፡ ቃቃህ፡ ከመ፡ ይፈርኅ፡ ኵሉ፡ ፍጥረት፡ 
                        እምገጸ፡ እግዚኡ፡ ከማሁ፡ ይፍርሁ፡ አጋንንት፡ እምገጸ፡ ገብርከ፡ 
                        <ref type="pers" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS14672GabraKrestos">ገብረ፡ ክርስቶስ፡</ref>
                     </incipit>
                  </msItem>
                  
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                     <locus from="2ra" to="2vb"/>
                     <title type="incomplete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT0303Malke">LIT0303Malke</title>
                     <note cert="high">It is unclear if the entire <foreign xml:lang="gez">malkəʾ</foreign>
                        is attested here or not.
                        The <foreign xml:lang="de">Vorlage</foreign> of this text is 
                        <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/UppEt1#a1">No item: UppEt1, could not check for a1</ref>.</note>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                        ሰ፡ ለዝክረ፡ ስምክሙ፡ በሰሌዳ፡ ሕይወት፡ ጽሑፍ፡
                        ወለስዕ<sic resp="JK">ረ</sic>ትክሙ፡ ሰ፡ ጠለ፡ አርያም፡ ውኩፍ፡
                        ኢያቄም፡ ወሓና፡ ዘገነተ፡ ጽባሕ፡ አእዋፍ፡
                        ከመ፡ እንብብ፡ ማኅሌትክሙ፡ ከሢተ፡ ልሳን፡ ወአፍ፡
                        መንፈ<sic resp="JK">ስ</sic>፡ አእምሮ፡ ዓዚዝ፡ ዲቤየ፡ ያዕርፍ፡
                     </incipit>
                  </msItem>
                  
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i3">
                     <locus from="2vb" to="3r"/>
                     <title type="incomplete">Arabic-Gəʿəz glossary</title>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez" otherLangs="ar"/>
                     <note cert="high">The <foreign xml:lang="de">Vorlage</foreign> of this text is most probably
                        <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/UppEt1#a2">No item: UppEt1, could not check for a2</ref>; however, the text has been enhanced compared
                        to the <foreign xml:lang="de">Vorlage</foreign> by the addition of the Arabic terms
                        written with Arabic characters.</note>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">ነገረ፡ ዐረቢ፡ ሎኅ፡ ብ፡ ታቦት፡ ፡ لوج ማዕጠንት፡ ሹሬ፡ شوره</incipit>
                  </msItem>
                  
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i4">
                     <locus target="#3v"/>
                     <title type="incomplete">Unclear note</title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">ስምዑ፡ እንግርክሙ፡ ዘወሀበ፡ ተስፋ፡ ለውሉደ፡ ሰብእ፡ እግዚእነ። 
                     ፴፡ ፻፡ ፻፡ ፻፡ በምዕራብ፡ ወምሥራቅ፡ በሰሜን፡ ወዳቡብ፡ ለዘ፡ ይጼሊ፡ በቤተ፡ ክርስቶያን፡ <gap reason="ellipsis"/></incipit>
                  </msItem>
                  
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i5">
                     <locus from="3v" to="4r"/>
                     <title type="complete">Magic prayer for <ref type="pers" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS10036Wansleb">Johann-Michael Wansleben</ref>, 
                        called <foreign xml:lang="gez">ዮሐንስ፡ ሚካኤል፡</foreign></title>
                     <note cert="high">The <foreign xml:lang="de">Vorlage</foreign> of this text is most probably
                        <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/UppEt1#a5">No item: UppEt1, could not check for a5</ref>; however, the beneficiary of the prayer has been changed.</note>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">በዮድ፡ ስሙ፡ ለእግዚአብሔር፡ እንዘ፡ ሰፍሑ፡ አብ፡ ወፋእሙ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis"/></incipit>
                     <explicit xml:lang="gez">አጋንንት፡ ከመ፡ ኢይቅረቡ፡ ኀበ፡ ነፍሱ፡ ወሥጋሁ፡ ለገብረ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ 
                     ዮሐንስ፡ ሚካኤል፡</explicit>
                  </msItem>
                  
